### Setup
### 1. Create a group
### 2. Create 2-3 users
### 3. Test adding removing group invitations
### 4. Test adding removing group members
### 5. Delete group and users

@baseurl = http://localhost:5000/api

###Set these variables after creation
@groupId = 69f10b774950e5f7a02f0356
@demonId = 69f10b7a4950e5f7a02f0358
@tenzId = 69f10b7e4950e5f7a02f035a


###1.
POST {{baseurl}}/groups
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "groupName": "Roommates 343",
    "groupGoal": "We promise to complete our chores on time"
}

